Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:07.63,hobo,,0,0,0,,Hamada's Holiday in Guam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:15.45,hobo,,0,0,0,,When you first get to know people,\Nthey keep a distance. About this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:20.38,hobo,,0,0,0,,Now, Dorians are close to me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:22.10,hobo,,0,0,0,,It almost hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:27.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,They're very close,\Nand I think they sometimes forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.53,hobo,,0,0,0,,...that I'm their senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.86,hobo,,0,0,0,,Talking in the middle of the night, part one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:42.13,hobo,,0,0,0,,"Hamada learns for the first time\Nabout when everyone met him."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:47.25,hobo,,0,0,0,,We met Downtown for the first time\Nopening for their program, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.90,hobo,,0,0,0,,When did you meet them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:53.90,hobo,,0,0,0,,For us, the opportunity to come\Nto Tokyo from Fukuoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:57.30,hobo,,0,0,0,,...was a talk show called Matsu-Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.86,hobo,,0,0,0,,We were M-1 Grand Prix semifinalists\Nand invited to be on Matsu-Shin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:07.13,hobo,,0,0,0,,We got invited with Pu & Mu and met\NHitoshi Matsumoto of Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.90,hobo,,0,0,0,,He asked, "Are you coming to Tokyo?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.63,hobo,,0,0,0,,We met Shinsuke Shimada there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:16.63,hobo,,0,0,0,,So we answered, "We would like to come but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:19.25,hobo,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto said we should,\Nand Shinsuke said to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:23.86,hobo,,0,0,0,,"You should let them open for your shows."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:25.48,hobo,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto answered,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:30.90,hobo,,0,0,0,,"I can't, since Hamada decides everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.38,hobo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:38.33,hobo,,0,0,0,,We decided to go to Tokyo that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:40.95,hobo,,0,0,0,,It must have been luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:43.48,hobo,,0,0,0,,Our first job was opening for Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:45.16,hobo,,0,0,0,,Which was HEY! HEY! HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:48.52,hobo,,0,0,0,,You opened for that show?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.80,hobo,,0,0,0,,From then on, we did it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:56.50,hobo,,0,0,0,,Now we're able to work on\Nvarious sets with Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:02:00.35,hobo,,0,0,0,,They often say their dressing rooms are separate,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.08,hobo,,0,0,0,,and when I heard that, I didn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:08.16,hobo,,0,0,0,,But it's true.\NThey're separated until filming begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.95,hobo,,0,0,0,,Our manager, Nagae.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:15.22,hobo,,0,0,0,,He's been with us for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:20.08,hobo,,0,0,0,,When he was a rookie dressed in a suit,\Nwe did our first opening act.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.66,hobo,,0,0,0,,He was still new to TV work then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.38,hobo,,0,0,0,,You were new too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:29.08,hobo,,0,0,0,,He asked what we're supposed to do,\Nbut it was our first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:30.70,hobo,,0,0,0,,None of us knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:34.62,hobo,,0,0,0,,The guy in the suit didn't know,\Nso we were at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:38.98,hobo,,0,0,0,,We decided to greet Downtown,\Nwho were in different dressing rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.06,0:02:44.93,hobo,,0,0,0,,We didn't know who to go see first,\NMatsumoto or Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:50.20,hobo,,0,0,0,,Someone told us where Matsumoto was,\Nso we decided to see him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.43,hobo,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto was reading a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:59.20,hobo,,0,0,0,,We said, "Our name is Dorians.\NWe'll be the opening act."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:03.66,hobo,,0,0,0,,And he answered, "Dorians? Oh, that's not good."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.52,hobo,,0,0,0,,We asked, "Not good?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:10.13,hobo,,0,0,0,,He said, "Well, I don't think that's good."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.72,hobo,,0,0,0,,I started sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.06,hobo,,0,0,0,,I didn't get it. He said, "Your name is not good."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,"Hamada is extremely mad about you guys."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.60,hobo,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.92,hobo,,0,0,0,,We went to see Matsumoto first,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:28.56,hobo,,0,0,0,,so we were late greeting Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.95,hobo,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. You didn't know how things worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:34.13,hobo,,0,0,0,,We were late greeting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.05,hobo,,0,0,0,,-Matsumoto just said that.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:39.26,hobo,,0,0,0,,We were told Hamada was angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.45,hobo,,0,0,0,,That's nerve-racking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:45.63,hobo,,0,0,0,,Our first TV work! We thought,\N"We had to greet Hamada first."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:50.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,Then Matsumoto advised,\N"You should go apologize."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:54.13,hobo,,0,0,0,,We thanked him and said we'd do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:57.55,hobo,,0,0,0,,We knocked on Hamada's door and apologized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:59.28,hobo,,0,0,0,,"We're truly sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.73,hobo,,0,0,0,,We could only say sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:06.60,hobo,,0,0,0,,We apologized about our name,\Nbut Hamada started laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.13,0:04:09.68,hobo,,0,0,0,,We were confused and didn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.98,hobo,,0,0,0,,We had just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.15,hobo,,0,0,0,,Hamada was laughing just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:17.26,hobo,,0,0,0,,He said, "Hang on." He yelled, "Matsumoto!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.18,hobo,,0,0,0,,He said to him, "What did you tell them?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:22.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,This was at a dressing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:27.40,hobo,,0,0,0,,He left his dressing room\Nand went over to where Matsumoto was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.28,hobo,,0,0,0,,"You must have said something!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:31.33,hobo,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:36.18,hobo,,0,0,0,,I knew right away by Dorians' behavior\Nthat he had said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.82,hobo,,0,0,0,,After he went there and came back,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:42.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,we were confused, saying, "What's happening?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:45.18,hobo,,0,0,0,,We were the only ones laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.86,hobo,,0,0,0,,We thought, "Downtown gets along well."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:53.10,hobo,,0,0,0,,I didn't get it, because I thought\Nthey didn't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:58.63,hobo,,0,0,0,,He smacked Matsumoto,\Nand everyone laughed, so I was confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:05.53,hobo,,0,0,0,,We asked Nagae if it was normal\Nto be pranked, but he didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:11.05,hobo,,0,0,0,,We asked the other crew,\Nand they said that never happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:16.50,hobo,,0,0,0,,They said Hamada never goes to see\NMatsumoto before a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.80,hobo,,0,0,0,,That was our first meeting with Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.58,hobo,,0,0,0,,The very first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.76,hobo,,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:31.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,They weren't scary.\NThey were kind and really got along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.30,hobo,,0,0,0,,That was our impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.48,hobo,,0,0,0,,My image of them changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:40.68,hobo,,0,0,0,,Even to this day,\NDowntown doesn't share a dressing room,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,so recalling it now, that was shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.40,hobo,,0,0,0,,That was the first and last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.43,hobo,,0,0,0,,The first and last time that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.15,hobo,,0,0,0,,-But you had met Hirai.\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:55.22,hobo,,0,0,0,,I brought him along when we went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:59.10,hobo,,0,0,0,,He was so nervous he ordered\Na rice omelet and plain rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.02,hobo,,0,0,0,,Of course I was nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.08,hobo,,0,0,0,,-Rice omelet and plain rice? Rice with rice?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.48,hobo,,0,0,0,,That's what he got.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.56,hobo,,0,0,0,,I told him to order something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.52,hobo,,0,0,0,,We went to Mishuku, the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:15.42,hobo,,0,0,0,,I had just gotten used to Inomoto,\Nthen Hamada showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.03,hobo,,0,0,0,,-And I invited you suddenly too.\N-Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:23.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,Hamada invited me to dinner,\Nso I asked if I could bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.95,hobo,,0,0,0,,He was shocked when I said\Nhe'd be seeing Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,That's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:35.46,hobo,,0,0,0,,He's relaxed now, sitting near Hamada\Nbanging his head on the chair laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,But at that dinner, he sat like a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,Of course, you'd be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,We all experienced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:48.46,hobo,,0,0,0,,All his replies sounded like hisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're leaking air.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.20,hobo,,0,0,0,,"Hiss..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:59.48,hobo,,0,0,0,,-"You're full?" "Hiss..."\N-Yeah, I really did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.75,hobo,,0,0,0,,Hamada told him\Nto order something, and Hamada said,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.35,hobo,,0,0,0,,"Hurry up and decide!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:08.92,hobo,,0,0,0,,So Hirai got a rice omelet,\Nand Hamada asked if it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.96,hobo,,0,0,0,,So he ordered plain rice too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.73,hobo,,0,0,0,,Hamada said, "You're weird."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:17.76,hobo,,0,0,0,,"Rice omelet and rice?" "Hiss."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.22,hobo,,0,0,0,,When did you meet Downtown?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.78,hobo,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.33,hobo,,0,0,0,,-You haven't met them yet?\N-Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:30.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,He's been sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.83,hobo,,0,0,0,,He's been sitting there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:40.08,hobo,,0,0,0,,I met Masayoshi long before Hirai.\NHe's the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:43.13,hobo,,0,0,0,,He met Hamada before all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,You were?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.22,hobo,,0,0,0,,It wasn't work related,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:52.10,hobo,,0,0,0,,but I was invited to Mishuku\Nwith Inomoto out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.50,hobo,,0,0,0,,I was surprised when he called.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.48,hobo,,0,0,0,,When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.63,hobo,,0,0,0,,A long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.45,hobo,,0,0,0,,You've known Hamada for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.73,hobo,,0,0,0,,He's the longest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.28,hobo,,0,0,0,,Over ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:09.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,You've been around for my moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:14.73,hobo,,0,0,0,,I ordered him to come to Shinjuku\Nand made him pack with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.70,hobo,,0,0,0,,-I packed for him.\N-You did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:22.48,hobo,,0,0,0,,Inomoto, you were at work,\Nand I had to get it done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.00,hobo,,0,0,0,,So you asked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:28.58,hobo,,0,0,0,,Inomoto used to look after me back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:32.88,hobo,,0,0,0,,and even though I lived far,\Nhe'd invite me out for drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:38.33,hobo,,0,0,0,,Inomoto told me to move closer,\Nso I moved close to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.76,hobo,,0,0,0,,We became closer after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:46.18,hobo,,0,0,0,,I'm not a graduate of Tokyo NSC.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:47.28,hobo,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:52.72,hobo,,0,0,0,,I entered Yoshimoto\Nas Ikuyo Kuruyo's apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:56.40,hobo,,0,0,0,,So surprisingly, Hamada\Nhas known Masayoshi for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.28,hobo,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:01.72,hobo,,0,0,0,,I think it's over 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.13,hobo,,0,0,0,,Masayoshi is the oldest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.76,hobo,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:09.42,hobo,,0,0,0,,We spend more time outside work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.70,hobo,,0,0,0,,I've never worked with Masayoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.46,hobo,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.62,hobo,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-After all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:22.48,hobo,,0,0,0,,He's done opening acts for some of my shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:25.92,hobo,,0,0,0,,No studio filming or on location?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.03,hobo,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:31.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,-I haven't.\N-So you haven't met Downtown yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.66,hobo,,0,0,0,,I thought so. Who is that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.68,hobo,,0,0,0,,-Not Hamada.\N-Right, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:41.13,hobo,,0,0,0,,We've opened for HEY! HEY! HEY! too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:46.86,hobo,,0,0,0,,We opened for most of Shinsuke's programs then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:50.23,hobo,,0,0,0,,Because he's my master's fellow pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:54.92,hobo,,0,0,0,,So we opened for all of\Nthe programs Shinsuke was involved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.80,hobo,,0,0,0,,That led to opening for Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:02.42,hobo,,0,0,0,,Once, Downtown hosted Shinsuke's program.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.26,hobo,,0,0,0,,To help him, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.68,hobo,,0,0,0,,We did the opening act then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:12.43,hobo,,0,0,0,,which led us to open for Downtown's\Nprograms like HEY! HEY! HEY!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:18.32,hobo,,0,0,0,,Back then, my impressions\Nof Hamada at work and outside of work...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.46,hobo,,0,0,0,,...were completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:23.50,hobo,,0,0,0,,We were still scared of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:29.76,hobo,,0,0,0,,Well, you two of Dorians have\Na different relationship with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:35.36,hobo,,0,0,0,,but I still feel a distance between Hamada and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:38.06,hobo,,0,0,0,,In your relationship with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.43,hobo,,0,0,0,,-I get nervous.\N-He was scary back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.35,hobo,,0,0,0,,-He was very scary.\N-Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:50.22,hobo,,0,0,0,,I still remember my master Ikuyo saying,\N"Hamada appears on TV like that,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.73,hobo,,0,0,0,,"but he's actually very reliable."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:57.46,hobo,,0,0,0,,She told me,\N"Don't mimic how rowdy he is on TV!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.10,hobo,,0,0,0,,-How's he in real life?\N-Rowdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.66,hobo,,0,0,0,,He was nothing like what Ikuyo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.33,hobo,,0,0,0,,-Just rowdy?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:12.50,hobo,,0,0,0,,We ate ramen yesterday, so I offered\Nto pour beer, but he said not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:17.50,hobo,,0,0,0,,He told me to just pour him beer\Nwhen he got too old to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.28,hobo,,0,0,0,,When the pot stickers came,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:22.38,hobo,,0,0,0,,he yelled at me to hurry with the soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:24.12,hobo,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.18,hobo,,0,0,0,,He's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:27.56,hobo,,0,0,0,,He's rowdy like Rambo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:32.65,hobo,,0,0,0,,-Rambo.\N-He's Rambo.

